            <article class="policy-content">

                <div class="intro-box">
                    <p>
                        By using this website, submitting information, or
                        placing an order, you acknowledge the practices
                        described in this Privacy Policy. This policy applies
                        to information collected through the Big Boss Bundles
                        website and related customer communications.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <section
                    class="policy-section"
                    id="information-collected"
                >

                    <h2>1. Information We May Collect</h2>

                    <p>
                        We may collect information that you voluntarily provide
                        when you place an order, request customer support,
                        subscribe to communications, participate in a promotion,
                        complete a form, or otherwise interact with Big Boss
                        Bundles.
                    </p>

                    <h3>Personal and Contact Information</h3>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Name</li>
                        <li>Email address</li>
                        <li>Telephone number</li>
                        <li>Billing address</li>
                        <li>Shipping address</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Order and Transaction Information</h3>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Products purchased or viewed</li>
                        <li>Order number and order history</li>
                        <li>Selected hair origin, texture, length, or shade</li>
                        <li>Shipping, delivery, or pickup details</li>
                        <li>Discounts, promotions, or gift information</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Device and Website Information</h3>

                    <p>
                        When you visit the website, certain information may be
                        collected automatically, including your IP address,
                        browser type, device type, referring page, pages viewed,
                        approximate location, and interactions with the website.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="how-used">

                    <h2>2. How We May Use Information</h2>

                    <p>
                        Big Boss Bundles may use personal information for
                        legitimate business purposes, including to:
                    </p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Process, fulfill, and deliver customer orders</li>

                        <li>
                            Provide order confirmations, shipping updates,
                            pickup information, and customer service
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Verify information, help prevent fraud, and protect
                            transactions
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Respond to questions, requests, disputes, or product
                            concerns
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Operate, maintain, personalize, and improve the
                            website
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Understand product interest and website performance
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Send promotional communications where permitted and
                            subject to customer choices
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Maintain business, tax, transaction, and compliance
                            records
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Enforce our Terms and Conditions, policies, and
                            legal rights
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="payments">

                    <h2>3. Payments and Order Processing</h2>

                    <p>
                        Payments may be processed through third-party payment
                        processors, banks, digital wallets, installment-payment
                        providers, or marketplace platforms selected for the
                        website.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Payment providers may collect and process payment-card,
                        billing, authentication, and transaction information
                        under their own privacy policies and security practices.
                        Big Boss Bundles may receive confirmation of payment,
                        transaction status, billing contact information, and
                        limited payment details needed to complete or service
                        an order.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Customers should review the privacy terms of any
                        third-party payment or marketplace service they choose
                        to use.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="cookies">

                    <h2>4. Cookies and Analytics</h2>

                    <p>
                        The website may use cookies, pixels, local storage,
                        analytics tools, and similar technologies to remember
                        preferences, maintain shopping-cart functionality,
                        understand website usage, improve performance, and
                        support marketing.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        You may be able to control certain cookies through your
                        browser settings. Disabling cookies may prevent some
                        website features from functioning properly.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="sharing">

                    <h2>5. How Information May Be Shared</h2>

                    <p>
                        Big Boss Bundles does not disclose personal information
                        merely for unrelated purposes. Information may be shared
                        with service providers when reasonably necessary to
                        operate the business, fulfill orders, or provide the
                        website.
                    </p>

                    <p>These recipients may include:</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Payment and fraud-prevention providers</li>
                        <li>Shipping carriers and delivery providers</li>
                        <li>Website hosting and technical-service providers</li>
                        <li>Email, communications, and customer-support tools</li>
                        <li>Analytics and advertising providers</li>
                        <li>Professional advisers and business consultants</li>
                        <li>
                            Government agencies or other parties when legally
                            required
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>
                        Information may also be disclosed when reasonably
                        necessary to protect customers, prevent fraud, enforce
                        policies, respond to legal process, or protect the
                        rights, property, and safety of Big Boss Bundles or
                        others.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="security">

                    <h2>6. Information Security</h2>

                    <p>
                        Big Boss Bundles seeks to use reasonable administrative,
                        technical, and physical safeguards appropriate to the
                        nature of the information maintained.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        However, no website, transmission method, payment
                        platform, or electronic-storage system can be guaranteed
                        to be completely secure. Customers should protect their
                        passwords, devices, and account information and should
                        contact us promptly regarding suspected unauthorized
                        activity involving an order.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="retention">

                    <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>

                    <p>
                        Information may be retained for as long as reasonably
                        necessary to process and document transactions, provide
                        customer service, comply with tax and accounting
                        obligations, resolve disputes, prevent fraud, enforce
                        agreements, and satisfy applicable legal requirements.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Retention periods may vary based on the type of
                        information, the reason it was collected, and applicable
                        business or legal obligations.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="privacy-rights">

                    <h2>8. Privacy Choices and Rights</h2>

                    <p>
                        Depending on your location and applicable law, you may
                        have the right to request access to, correction of,
                        deletion of, or information about certain personal data.
                        You may also have rights concerning certain processing
                        or disclosures of personal data.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        To submit a privacy request, contact Big Boss Bundles
                        using the information below. We may need to verify your
                        identity before completing a request. Certain
                        information may be retained when necessary to complete
                        transactions, comply with law, protect security, prevent
                        fraud, or establish and defend legal rights.
                    </p>

                    <h3>Marketing Communications</h3>

                    <p>
                        You may unsubscribe from promotional emails by using the
                        unsubscribe option included in the communication or by
                        contacting us. Transactional messages concerning an
                        order, payment, shipping, pickup, or customer-service
                        request may still be sent.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="children">

                    <h2>9. Children’s Privacy</h2>

                    <p>
                        This website is intended for a general audience and is
                        not directed to children under 13. Big Boss Bundles does
                        not knowingly request or collect personal information
                        from children under 13 through this website.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        A parent or legal guardian who believes a child has
                        submitted personal information may contact us to request
                        review and appropriate deletion.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="third-party-links">

                    <h2>10. Third-Party Platforms and Links</h2>

                    <p>
                        The website may contain links to Instagram, TikTok,
                        Facebook, Amazon, TikTok Shop, payment services, shipping
                        services, and other third-party websites or platforms.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Big Boss Bundles does not control the privacy practices,
                        content, or security of third-party services. Their own
                        privacy policies and terms apply when you use those
                        services.
                    </p>

                </section>

                <section class="policy-section" id="changes">

                    <h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

                    <p>
                        Big Boss Bundles may update this Privacy Policy to
                        reflect operational, legal, technological, or business
                        changes. The effective date at the top of this page will
                        be updated when material revisions are published.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Continued use of the website after an updated policy is
                        posted means that the updated policy will apply to
                        subsequent website use, subject to applicable law.
                    </p>

                </section>

